                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt/>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>Prepared at Mossy Creek Academy; daily temperature, wind,
                precipitation.</summary>
            </div>
            <pageNote/>
        </page>
        <page n="02" image="va.au.ss.1857.04.29.02">
            <div type="a">
                <column>1</column>
                <head>To the Patrons of the Staunton Spectator</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt/>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names>
                    <name>
                        <ln>Mauzy</ln>
                        <pf>Richard</pf>
                    </name>
                    <name>
                        <ln>Waddell</ln>
                        <pf>J. A.</pf>
                    </name>
                    <name>
                        <ln>Waddell</ln>
                        <pf>L.</pf>
                    </name>
                </names>
                <summary>Agreement made between Mauzy and SS to merge the True American into the SS,
                    effective 5/1/57. Mauzy will be a joint proprietor. True American subscribers
                    will now receive the SS. SS will also tighten up subscriptions--payment now
                    required in advance.</summary>
            </div>
